step_data.thought: I now have the filters panel open. To identify inactive customer accounts created before 2022, I need to set up two filters: 1) Customer Since (before 2022) and 2) Account status (inactive). Looking at the available filter options, I can see the 'Customer Since' filter where I can set a date range. I need to set the 'to' field to '12/31/2021' to capture all accounts created before 2022. I'll start by filling out the 'Customer Since' 'to' field with this date.
